OL,3,CFarage condemns 'ugly' comments by
OL,4,CReform UK MP but denies they're racist
OL,6,FNigel Farage has said comments made by
OL,7,FReform UK MP Sarah Pochin about ethnic
OL,8,Fminorities on TV adverts were "ugly",
OL,9,Fbut has refused to say they were
OL,10,Fracist.
OL,12,FThe Reform leader has been under
OL,13,Fpressure to suspend Pochin, the MP for
OL,14,FRuncorn and Helsby, after she told a
OL,15,Fmedia phone-in that it drives her
OL,16,F"mad" to "see adverts full of black
OL,17,Fpeople, full of Asian people".
