OL,3,CFarage condemns 'ugly' comments by
OL,4,CReform UK MP but denies they're racist
OL,6,FDuring an appearance on TalkTV, Pochin
OL,7,Fadded that "it doesn't reflect our
OL,8,Fsociety" and "your average white
OL,9,Fperson, average white family is... not
OL,10,Frepresented any more".
OL,12,FThe MP has since apologised, saying
OL,13,Fher comments had been "phrased
OL,14,Fpoorly", but appeared to stand by the
OL,15,Fsentiment.
OL,17,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer said
OL,18,FFarage had "questions to answer" over
OL,19,Fwhat he labelled an example of
OL,20,F"shocking racism".
