OL,3,CFarage condemns 'ugly' comments by
OL,4,CReform UK MP but denies they're racist
OL,6,F"I understand the basic point, but the
OL,7,Fway she put it, the way she worded it,
OL,8,Fwas wrong and was ugly, and if I
OL,9,Fthought that the intention behind it
OL,10,Fwas racist, I would have taken a lot
OL,11,Fmore action than I have to date."
OL,13,FStarmer, speaking to broadcasters
OL,14,Fduring a visit to Turkey on Monday,
OL,15,Fwas asked whether Pochin had been
OL,16,Fracist to make the remarks.
