OL,3,CFarage condemns 'ugly' comments by
OL,4,CReform UK MP but denies they're racist
OL,6,F"Yes, she was," he said. "It's
OL,7,Fshocking racism and it's the sort of
OL,8,Fthing that will tear our country
OL,9,Fapart, and it tells you everything
OL,10,Fabout Reform.
OL,12,F"Nigel Farage has got some questions
OL,13,Fto answer, because either he doesn't
OL,14,Fconsider it racist, which in my view
OL,15,Fis shocking in itself, or he does
OL,16,Fthink it's racist and he's shown
OL,17,Fabsolutely no leadership.
