OL,3,CFarage condemns 'ugly' comments by
OL,4,CReform UK MP but denies they're racist
OL,6,F"I'm the prime minister of the whole
OL,7,Fof our country, our reasonable,
OL,8,Ftolerant, diverse country, and I want
OL,9,Fto serve the whole country.
OL,11,F"He can't even call out racism."
OL,13,FIn a statement following her initial
OL,14,Fremarks, Pochin claimed she had been
OL,15,Ftrying to say the advertising industry
OL,16,Fhad gone "DEI (diversity, equity and
OL,17,Finclusion) mad".
OL,19,F"My comments were phrased poorly and I
OL,20,Fapologise for any offence caused,
OL,21,Fwhich was not my intention," she said.
